1992;;Just like a Woman;;British;;Christopher Monger;;Julie Walters, Adrian Pasdar, Paul Freeman;;comedy/drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Just_like_a_Woman_(1992_film);;Gerald Tilson, a finance executive, finds himself thrown out by his wife when she discovers women's underwear in their flat; in fact the clothes belong to him. He takes lodgings with Monica, who gradually discovers his alter ego, "Geraldine". A subplot deals with his boss' plan to defraud their Japanese clients, and how the couple thwart it.